<section id="secfhsst_id4698"><title>Rotasie</title>
        <list id="id74922" display="block" list-type="enumerated"><item id="uid66">Doen die volgende vir elke rotasie om die oorsprong:
(i) Skryf die toepaslike reël neer.
(ii) Teken 'n diagram wat die rigting van die rotasie aandui.
<list id="id74950" display="block" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item id="uid67">OA word geroteer na OA<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> met A(4;2) en A<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>(-2;4)
</item><item id="uid68">OB word geroteer na OB<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> met B(-2;5) en B<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>(5;2)
</item><item id="uid69">OC word geroteer na OC<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> met C(-1;-4) en C<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>(1;4)
</item></list></item>
          <item id="uid70">Kopieer<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>Δ</m:mi></m:math>XYZ op grafiekpapier. Die koördinate word op die figuur aangedui.
<list id="id75093" display="block" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item id="uid71">Roteer <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>Δ</m:mi></m:math>XYZ antikloksgewys deur 'n hoek van 90<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>∘</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> om die oorsprong om die volgende te kry <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>Δ</m:mi></m:math>X<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>Y<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>Z<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>. Dui die koördinate van X<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>, Y<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> en Z<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> aan.
</item><item id="uid72">Roteer <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>Δ</m:mi></m:math>XYZ deur 180<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>∘</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> om die oorsprong om die volgende te kry <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>Δ</m:mi></m:math>X<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>Y<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>Z<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>. Dui die koördinate van X<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math>, Y<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> en Z<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msup><m:mrow/><m:mo>'</m:mo></m:msup></m:math> aan.
</item></list><figure id="id75418"><label>Figuur</label><media id="id75418_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/MG11C16_032.png" id="id75418_onlineimage" width="195"><!-- NOTE: attribute width changes image size online (pixels). original width is 195. --></image><image mime-type="application/postscript" for="pdf" src="../../media/MG11C16_032.eps" id="id75418_printimage"/></media></figure></item>
        </list>
        
